  <title>The Natural Base</title>

<commentary audience="instructor"><title>Overview</title>
<p>In this Lesson we briefly introduce the natural exponential and natural log functions. We consider their graphs and solving equations, and we write exponential growth and decay functions with base <m>e</m>.</p></commentary>

